  "text": "We propose a compatible neural architecture for translating into MRLs. The model benefits from subword-and character-level information and improves upon the state-of-the-art model of [CITATION_1] . We manipulated the model to incorporate morphological information and developed three new extensions, which are discussed in Sections 3.1, 3.2, and 3.3.",
